text: EXCLUSIVE: President Trump has told people close to him that he’s getting his lawyers to look into the Mary Trump matter, to explore what could be done in the way of legal retribution—or at least a threat—likely in the form of a cease and desist letter https://t.co/zoT0zhbP0M

name: thedailybeast
text: One source said the president appeared irked by news of Mary Trump's book and at one point mentioned that she had signed an NDA years ago https://t.co/zoT0zhbP0M

name: thedailybeast
text: The NDA states she is not allowed to publish anything regarding the litigation disputing Fred Trump’s estate or her relationship with Donald, Maryanne and Robert https://t.co/zoT0zhbP0M

name: thedailybeast
text: In the book, Mary Trump is expected to discuss difficult internal family dynamics and offer revelations about a younger Donald Trump as well as out herself as a primary source behind a New York Times investigation into her uncle’s taxes https://t.co/zoT0zhbP0M
